  "informal_statement": "For plane vectors u=(a,b) and v=(c,d), |u+v|^2 + |u-v|^2 = 2|u|^2 + 2|v|^2.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Expand both squared-distance sums to the same polynomial; `ring`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem parallelogram_law (a b c d : ℝ) : (a + c) ^ 2 + (b + d) ^ 2 + ((a - c) ^ 2 + (b - d) ^ 2) = 2 * (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2) + 2 * (c ^ 2 + d ^ 2)",
